hackathon-description-text: Come together with the Swarthmore community and build awesome technology for 12 hours! Meals and swag provided, snazzy prizes to be won. Hacking will commence in SCI 101.
hackathon-rules: As an Major League Hacking sactioned event, all MLH rules and code of conduct apply :)

Bluetooth speaker for each team member
Beats Wireless Headphones for each team member
$4000 Partial Scholarship to Horizons School of Technology for each member, Drone
